**Target Ratios (guidelines):**

- **Unit Tests:** 60-70% (Vitest)
- **Component/Integration Tests:** 25-35% (Testing Library + MSW)
- **E2E Tests:** 5-10% (Playwright)

**Required in Every LLM Output:**

